data.description: Welcome to this charming and beautifully maintained 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom traditional home, perfectly situated on a large lot in the heart of town. Boasting a blend of classic design and modern upgrades, this residence offers a comfortable and inviting living experience. Step inside to discover the warm ambiance of hardwood flooring throughout, creating an elegant and timeless appeal.  Schedule your showing today and envision yourself living in this picturesque traditional home with its abundant space, two fireplaces, and a renovated kitchen.
